# gates/

Compiled at the end of each implementation commit:

- `tsc.txt` — `npx tsc --noEmit` output
- `vitest-summary.txt` — `npm test -- --reporter=verbose` summary
- `semgrep.json` — `npx semgrep --config p/typescript --json` output
- `dependency-audit.json` — `npm audit --omit=dev --json` output
